          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGdX8Y9LbFocxG6qBz_UpfzeIuvMI797Lu2-Jcer5GxsQV3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Had a miscommunication around arriving right when they were closing but the store was very nice and replied to my review, which I appreciate. They have always been very kind in the past and I was under a lot of stress about a medication, and it sounds like they did not intend to close the gate on me. This goes a long way and I will continue to come here to support local business.",
