        {
          "username": "Hadassah Diaz",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "114807923985556760029",
          "user_review_count": 9,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjQDPCn0C1ibRdjloWbmXL447NniVvhjh5gwMmUnEHs8Z3UkD1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "They are the nicest people.  They discussed my medication issue at length.  They also  explained why they carry wonderful toys for children saying they were from the community and  had noticed that our Chinatown was devoid of learning toys for little ones. It is great when a local business cares about all aspects of a community.  Bravo Corner Chemists!",
